              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Herald of Frost</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/2575ddfaacc7015ebab2d17fba4593ea_1850377101346238174.png",
                "id": "talent45960",
                "key": "Adeptus Art: Herald of Frost",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptus Art: Herald of Frost"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fortune-Preserving Talisman</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fortune-Preserving Talisman</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character uses a Skill: </span>If that character does not have full HP, heal that character for 2 HP.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/900dec327166a00218479cf8616072fc_3384695038743298855.png",
                "id": "talent90772",
                "key": "Adeptus Art: Preserver of Fortune",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptus Art: Preserver of Fortune"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this Summon is on the field, after Qiqi uses Normal Attack: </span>Heals your character that took the most DMG for 1 HP. Once each Round, additionally heal your active character for 1 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1a3db5c5531fb4444758f49100411b27_4758209360887920465.png",
                "id": "talent46612",
                "key": "Herald of Frost",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/27/35428890/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_5797755198810302162.png",
                "title": "Herald of Frost"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/b4a5f3f562110b550fbd31015296cc35_7823418398022917631.png",
                "id": "talent33580",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1fafbff4b60b57a39c1f9a8c226a3a6b_9014124275114892229.png",
